# Scope of this shard:
#   - Modern-AI architecture / optimizer / training-trick experiments
#     each tested against n=6 anchors (n=6, σ=12, τ=4, φ=2, sopfr=5, J₂=24)
#   - Sub-families:
#       § A  Attention variants    (FlashAttn3, GQA-6, FFT-mix, Ring, Egyptian)
#       § B  Sequence models       (Mamba2, RWKV6, Hyena, Jamba, Griffin)
#       § C  MoE / sparse routing  (GShard/Switch, MoE-E8, Egyptian-MoE, partition)
#       § D  Training / optimizer  (BT54-AdamW-β2, LoRA-r8, Carmichael-LR,
#                                   Mertens-dropout, optimizer-constants-n6)
#       § E  Quant / compression   (4-bit, BitNet, MLA, KV-cache)
