#       § G  h_ee_* probes         (combined arch / FFN ratio / depth /
#                                   r-spectrum / head-dim / τ-predictor)
#       § H  Cross / verify        (verify_ai_algorithm_n6, verify_llm_improvement_n6)
#
# Honesty triad (mirrored from n6-arch shard 2026-04-26):
#   - Cycle-witness PASS preserved verbatim from source .hexa
#   - STUB / pending / NEAR / FALSIFIED preserved verbatim — never upgraded
#   - F-MOLT-A 5th/6th sample patterns preserved
#   - Source corpus state: ~55 of 62 are STUB (hypothesis-only, GPU/torch
#     dependency unresolved). Only 2 files emit a numerical dry-run verdict
#     (LoRA r=8, MoE E=8 top-2). The rest are graded [7] heuristic-pending.
#
# Grade policy (per task):
#   [10*]              analytical exact-match (rare here)
#   [10]               EMPIRICAL strict pass (dry-run with closed-form output)
#   [10*FAIL_DOC]      documented falsifier-fired (none in this corpus)
#   [9]                NEAR
#   [7]                heuristic extraction — STUB hypothesis (pending GPU run)
#
# Prefix: AIEFF-EXP-* (avoids collision with HEXA-AIEF / BT-* anchors
# already in atlas.n6 line 20644-20660 — Transformer L=σ=12, σ²=144, FFN=4·d,
# 6-bit quant 4-pillar are NOT re-emitted; this shard captures
# experiment-level facts only).
